video.title: Dynasty
video.synopsis: The Carringtons and the Colbys feud for control over their fortune -- and their children -- in this updated reboot of the classic prime-time soap.

episodes.synopsis: After coming to blows over business with her stepmother to be, an ever-ambitious Fallon sets her sights on her father's biggest rival.
episodes.title: I Hardly Recognized You

episodes.synopsis: All eyes are on the Carringtons in the wake of the Windbriar accident, prompting Blake to call a family meeting. Fallon helps hide Cristal's affair.
episodes.title: Spit It Out

episodes.synopsis: Suspicions swirl as Steven faces serious charges. Blake files a cease and desist order against Fallon. Anders confronts Cristal about her past.
episodes.title: Guilt Is for Insecure People

episodes.synopsis: In the wake of the robbery, Cristal lures Blake away for a weekend in the woods. Fallon goes after a big contract, and Steven works to clear his name.
episodes.title: Private as a Circus

episodes.synopsis: Cristal and Fallon compete for a high-profile magazine cover -- and the honor of being "Woman of the Year." Steven's ex-boyfriend returns to town.
episodes.title: Company Slut

episodes.synopsis: With Fallon on the outs, Cristal opens the family home to a recuperating houseguest and pays man-child Sammy Jo to take on baby-sitting duties.
episodes.title: I Only Exist for Me

episodes.synopsis: Thanksgiving with the Carringtons is a full-scale affair with football, food -- and family drama. Cristal's houseguest serves up a shocking surprise.
episodes.title: A Taste of Your Own Medicine

episodes.synopsis: Cristal's past comes back to haunt her just in time for the holidays. The Carringtons clash over client gifts before the city's annual tree lighting.
episodes.title: The Best Things in Life

episodes.synopsis: Forget calm and bright. Christmas at the Carringtons' brings unexpected guests, shocking scandals and a catfight under the tree.
episodes.title: Rotten Things

episodes.synopsis: Fallon plans an epic birthday party with gold-plated everything -- down to the wait staff. Sammy Jo comes face to face with a ghost from his past.
episodes.title: A Well Dressed Tarantula

episodes.synopsis: Blake insists on taking the lead on a covert rescue mission when he learns that Fallon's been kidnapped. But he can't do it all alone.
episodes.title: I Answer to No Man

episodes.synopsis: The stakes are high at a casino-themed political fundraiser, where Cristal suspects Blake's been bluffing, and Fallon goes all-in for a deal.
episodes.title: Promises You Can’t Keep

episodes.synopsis: Jeff and Monica put their payback plan in motion, Sammy Jo stages a next-level girls’ night, and Steven preps for a political run.
episodes.title: Nothing But Trouble

episodes.synopsis: Ted's messy exit puts Steven in a compromising position. Cecil moves from prison to paradise, and Culhane and Fallon dine with the Colbys.
episodes.title: The Gospel According to Blake Carrington

episodes.synopsis: Fallon plows forward with her plans for the wedding of the century, complete with ornamental peacocks. Sammy Jo hustles to secure his status.
episodes.title: Our Turn Now

episodes.synopsis: The Carringtons move from a wedding to a funeral, forcing Blake to confront painful emotions. Steven steps in to help Sammy Jo, and Jeff declares war.
episodes.title: Poor Little Rich Girl

episodes.synopsis: An estranged Carrington claws her way back home after an 11-year absence, shaking up the family estate and sending Blake into a vengeful rage.
episodes.title: Enter Alexis

episodes.synopsis: It's Fallon versus Alexis -- with a conflicted Steven caught in the middle. Elsewhere, Culhane and Cristal tend to a family crisis.
episodes.title: Don’t Con a Con Artist

episodes.synopsis: Fallon's power struggle with her mother heats up when Alexis interferes with her love life. Cristal asks Blake to do the right thing.
episodes.title: Use or Be Used

episodes.synopsis: While Alexis sets the stage for her next move, Fallon and Cristal forge a surprising partnership, and Anders helps Sammy Jo plan the perfect wedding.
episodes.title: A Line from the Past

episodes.synopsis: Fallon tries to take the company in a new direction while Jeff and Monica look into Alexis's claims. A surprise houseguest gets mixed reviews.
episodes.title: Trashy Little Tramp

episodes.synopsis: Steven and Sammy Jo's wedding attracts drama -- and uninvited guests. Fallon's power play hits a wall when the Colbys show up with surprising news.
episodes.title: Dead Scratch

episodes.synopsis: Fallon weighs multiple offers while Blake mourns a crushing loss. Steven wants to be honest with Sammy Jo but worries more bad news will break him.
episodes.title: Twenty-Three Skidoo

episodes.synopsis: Blake makes a big announcement, and Kirby cozies up to the Colbys. Fallon gets to know the Van Kirks -- but the family tree is swarming with snakes.
episodes.title: Ship of Vipers

episodes.synopsis: Culhane does business on Fallon's behalf, and Blake gets to know the "new" Cristal. Sammy Jo throws a blowout baby shower, and Kirby digs into her past.
episodes.title: The Butler Did It

episodes.synopsis: After an earth-shattering reveal at home, the Carringtons gather for quality time abroad -- quite unexpectedly. Culhane goes on a dangerous assignment.
episodes.title: Snowflakes in Hell

episodes.synopsis: A psychic comes to dinner with unsettling news. Jeff and Culhane forge an unlikely friendship, and Fallon suggests a "conscious uncoupling."
episodes.title: Queen of Cups

episodes.synopsis: When bad weather -- more specifically, a tornado -- brings everyone together for a dark and stormy Thanksgiving, Fallon finds there's no place like home.
episodes.title: That Witch

episodes.synopsis: Cristal and Blake celebrate new beginnings, leaving Alexis to indulge in some master manipulation. Elsewhere, Fallon pursues a passion project.
episodes.title: A Temporary Infestation

episodes.synopsis: Fallon pulls Alexis into wedding planning -- then pushes her out. With Steven in South America, Sammy Jo gets dangerously close to a member of the staff.
episodes.title: A Real Instinct for the Jugular

episodes.synopsis: It's a very Carrington Christmas as Blake and Fallon butt heads over the best way to handle a kidnapping, and Cristal suspects Alexis of hiding secrets.
episodes.title: Crazy Lady

episodes.synopsis: A desperate Culhane leans on Fallon for protection. Meanwhile, Cristal's got big news -- but she's reluctant to share it with Blake.
episodes.title: A Champagne Mood

episodes.synopsis: While Fallon gathers a squad for a "girls trip" on the slopes, Blake goes to Culhane with a job offer. Alexis takes a sad Sam under her wing.
episodes.title: The Sight of You

episodes.synopsis: With his relationship with Steven on shaky ground, Sam works toward self-improvement. A jilted Fallon tries to prove she's still got game.
episodes.title: Filthy Games

episodes.synopsis: Blake and Cristal are closer than ever -- until a surprise houseguest shakes their foundation. Culhane and Fallon come to blows at the office.
episodes.title: Even Worms Can Procreate

episodes.synopsis: Fallon and Sam fly to Paris and make a sobering discovery. A devastating loss moves Blake to take matters into his own hands.
episodes.title: Parisian Legend Has It…

episodes.synopsis: An unexpected guest puts a kink in Fallon's plans to shield Blake from family drama. Culhane and Cristal team up to solve a business problem.
episodes.title: Motherly Overprotectiveness

episodes.synopsis: When bad publicity puts the family name in jeopardy, Fallon rewrites her personal brand. Blake throws a lavish party to toast his son's return.
episodes.title: Miserably Ungrateful Men

episodes.synopsis: Fallon's fledgling publishing company is hungry to ink new deals -- but first, she'll have to deal with her past. Jeff makes a move at Atlantix.
episodes.title: How Two-Faced Can You Get?

episodes.synopsis: Adam unveils the new Alexis to the world at a lavish soirée for Sam -- who's newly single. Fallon gets involved in Liam's love life.
episodes.title: Life Is a Masquerade Party

episodes.synopsis: Liam’s mother makes a shocking announcement, and Jeff's health takes a turn for the worse. Cristal and Blake play Bonnie and Clyde.
episodes.title: This Illness of Mine

episodes.synopsis: Fallon teams up with Liam to take Adam down in front of Blake. Jeff and Monica's mother comes home, and Sam forces Anders to take a vacation.
episodes.title: New Lady in Town

episodes.synopsis: A reluctant Fallon agrees to cover for her father, and Sam goes on a spending spree. Cristal's forced to choose between Blake and her family.
episodes.title: Thicker Than Money

episodes.synopsis: As dark secrets come to light, the Carringtons must choose between protecting their family dynasty and preserving personal relationships.
episodes.title: Deception, Jealousy and Lies

episodes.synopsis: The Carrington fundraiser gala gets upstaged by drama when two bodies are pulled from the estate lake, dredging up disastrous family secrets.
episodes.title: Guilt Trip to Alaska

episodes.synopsis: Blake's troubles set off sneaky power plays between Cristal and Adam. At Liam's bedside in the hospital, Fallon is stunned by a rude surprise.
episodes.title: Caution Never Won a War

episodes.synopsis: Sam has a crisis of conscience when he learns about his hotel's unsettling history. Fallon gets her hands dirty when she starts community service.
episodes.title: Wild Ghost Chase

episodes.synopsis: Music — and leaking gas — are in the air at the manor for the winery event. Adam's mischief goes sideways along with Fallon's scheme to win Liam back.
episodes.title: Something Desperate

episodes.synopsis: Blindsided by his setback, Adam leans on a new ally. Sam stresses his hotel opening, and Fallon mends her broken heart by getting back to business.
episodes.title: Mother? I'm at La Mirage

episodes.synopsis: Blake and Cristal's plot for his trial hits a snag when Jeff gets suspicious. Back in entrepreneur mode, Fallon considers a pitch from Dominique.
episodes.title: A Used Up Memory

episodes.synopsis: A kinder, gentler Blake gives his scheming family members pause at Thanksgiving. Blinded by love, Adam plays into one of Fallon's devious plots.
episodes.title: Shoot from the Hip

episodes.synopsis: Adam and Fallon's feuding triggers a major memory for Liam. Blake's trial takes a stunning turn when a surprise witness takes the stand.
episodes.title: The Sensational Blake Carrington Trial

episodes.synopsis: Blake makes a risky gamble with his trial's new witness before Fallon tricks Cristal into a big reveal. Jeff finds a fierce ally to help get revenge.
episodes.title: The Caviar, I Trust, Is Not Burned

episodes.synopsis: A changed Adam starts a new chapter while Fallon makes her own big move. Cristal is shattered by a secret from Alexis. Jeff's condition worsens.
episodes.title: What Sorrows Are You Drowning?

episodes.synopsis: Cristal rages over Alexis's revelation while "Captain Blake" steers his way back toward Atlanta's elite. Jeff and Alexis prove a mighty power couple.
episodes.title: A Wound That May Never Heal

episodes.synopsis: Fallon's fake house-hunting persona leads to real honesty with Liam. Dominique plays dirty with Michael. Blake's blackmail hits Jeff where it hurts.
episodes.title: Battle Lines

episodes.synopsis: Cristal and Blake's new roomie makes problems and green juice. Sam's love life gets complicated. Liam's dream project flips the script for Fallon.
episodes.title: You See Most Things in Terms of Black and White

episodes.synopsis: Liam and Fallon get caught in a parent trap. Dominique's betrayal — and business savvy — take Vanessa aback. Adam comes clean about a dirty deed.
episodes.title: That Wicked Stepmother

episodes.synopsis: Michael can't tell the difference between the real and reality-show Vanessas. Adam and Alexis "help" a sick Jeff. Fallon works out some mommy issues.
episodes.title: Up a Tree

episodes.synopsis: Cristal and Blake's road to redemption hits some bumps. A confession from Heidi adds a twist to Liam's family tree. Hope fades for Jeff's health.
episodes.title: Is the Next Surgery on the House?

episodes.synopsis: A star is born when Alexis helps Fallon do damage control over some bad press. Blake and Laura hatch a scheme. Kirby and Sam's partnership is tested.
episodes.title: She Cancelled …

episodes.synopsis: Blake and Cristal's sins jeopardize their marriage. Fallon's full of surprises at the Carrington Cares fundraiser. A bromance blooms for Sam and Jeff.
episodes.title: You Make Being a Priest Sound Like Something Bad

episodes.synopsis: A business deal gone wrong endangers Anders and Blake. With a reality TV hit on her hands, Dominique plays hardball. Adam's daddy issues take a turn.
episodes.title: Robin Hood Rescues

episodes.synopsis: Fallon's bachelorette party brings all kinds of headaches. Jeff rethinks his deal with Alexis. A worried Anders starts digging into Adam's dark past.
episodes.title: My Hangover's Arrived

episodes.synopsis: An unwelcome arrival adds to Fallon’s wedding planning woes. Business and pleasure mix up trouble for Blake. Dominique makes a key discovery.
episodes.title: That Unfortunate Dinner

episodes.synopsis: Alexis and Jeff play hardball with Blake. Twists of fate threaten Fallon and Liam’s nuptials, while someone plots to kill the mood completely.
episodes.title: Vows Are Still Sacred

episodes.synopsis: Reeling from the wedding-day disasters, Carrington Manor must triage multiple crises. Cristal feels torn about how to move forward.
episodes.title: The Aftermath

episodes.synopsis: The honeymoon doesn’t last long for Liam and Fallon, as a nasty feud makes drama at the manor. Michael threatens to go public with a damning discovery.
episodes.title: Everybody Loves the Carringtons

episodes.synopsis: Michael enlists Sam to lay a trap for the league commissioner. Fallon’s rebrand plans sputter. Blake plays God with Cristal’s love life.
episodes.title: New Hopes, New Beginnings

episodes.synopsis: Blake and Fallon’s role reversal tests her leadership — and patience. Sam devises an elaborate scheme to keep Ryan in Atlanta.
episodes.title: A Little Father-Daughter Chat

episodes.synopsis: To distract Liam while she finalizes a deal, Fallon invites an old friend of his to town. Alexis sets her sights on splitting up Adam and Kirby.
episodes.title: The Birthday Party

episodes.synopsis: One of Sam’s former flames reappears. A tricky love triangle takes shape between Michael, Jeff and Mia. Cristal shares shocking news with Adam.
episodes.title: Your Sick and Self-Serving Vendetta

episodes.synopsis: Trapped together, Alexis and Dominique bare teeth — and then their souls. Adam and Cristal keep her painful secret. Corinne confesses her real motives.
episodes.title: Equal Justice for the Rich

episodes.synopsis: Fallon coerces Jeff into scheming and spying. Manipulated by Oliver, Kirby makes risky choices. A night out at the club goes sideways for Sam.
episodes.title: I Hate to Spoil Your Memories

episodes.synopsis: Adam crosses the line to get Cristal an experimental treatment. Dominique confronts an ugly truth about the fashion industry.
episodes.title: A Public Forum for Her Lies

episodes.synopsis: Dead set on exposing the scandal linked to his father’s death, Liam treads on dangerous ground. Michael and Sam weigh a deal with the devil.
episodes.title: Everything but Facing Reality

episodes.synopsis: Who is in the casket? At an outdoor funeral, flashbacks reveal clues as multiple members of the Carrington Manor clan face deadly threats.
episodes.title: Go Rescue Someone Else

episodes.synopsis: Reeling from a devastating loss, members of the Carrington inner circle try to move on. Dominique angles to promote her fashion line.
episodes.title: But I Don't Need Therapy

episodes.synopsis: Fallon hustles to get her shopping network off the ground. Blake scrambles to save his sputtering airline. Dominique comes through for Cristal.
episodes.title: She Lives in a Showplace Penthouse

episodes.synopsis: Blake storms onto the campaign trail. Sam grapples with guilt while Michael pushes their business forward. A mysterious stranger trails Alexis.
episodes.title: The British Are Coming

episodes.synopsis: Fallon’s shopping network wears on her marriage while Colin plots a coup. Amanda looks for answers. Jeff and Michael make peace — and a devious plan.
episodes.title: Stars Make You Smile

episodes.synopsis: Suspicious of Amanda’s motives, Fallon digs for dirt. Cristal gets alarming news from Beto. Trailing in the polls, Blake recruits reluctant helpers.
episodes.title: A Good Marriage in Every Sense

episodes.synopsis: Amanda and Adam’s sibling rivalry ramps up. Attempting a cover-up, Michael and Sam make things worse. Fallon and Liam’s marriage reaches a crossroads.
episodes.title: Everything Looks Wonderful, Joseph

episodes.synopsis: Now both working at the hospital, Adam and Amanda are out for blood. Eva foils Fallon’s plans to fix things with Liam. Sam confronts Cristal and Blake.
episodes.title: You Vicious, Miserable Liar

episodes.synopsis: Fallon and Liam bring heavy baggage on a couple’s retreat to patch things up. A power-hungry Alexis uses Brady to get at Dominique. Dr. Adam does harm.
episodes.title: Affairs of State and Affairs of the Heart

episodes.synopsis: Secrets, suspicion and subterfuge set the stage for Blake’s big political rally at La Mirage, leading to a shocking turn of events.
episodes.title: Filled With Manipulations and Deceptions
